headline: PH Q2 Deep Dive: Aerospace Momentum and Margin Expansion Lead Results
summary: Industrial machinery company Parker-Hannifin (NYSE:PH) reported Q2 CY2025 results exceeding the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 1.1% year on year to $5.24 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $7.69 per share was 8.6% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
